data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living at 7327 Embassy Trace in Riverdale, GA. Built in 2020, this meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home sits on a large corner lot. The clean, contemporary interior features a walk-in pantry for added convenience, creating a spacious and welcoming atmosphere. Upstairs, a versatile loft area adds to the home's flexibility. The property not only offers a stylish and well-maintained living space but also benefits from a well-kept exterior, contributing to its curb appeal. Nestled in a thriving neighborhood and conveniently located near schools, parks, and amenities, this home is a perfect blend of comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make 7327 Embassy Trace your homeCoa 2020 gem in an ideal Riverdale location!
